I became an abbot

550
00:25:19,833 --> 00:25:22,500
I was the golden body right there
The Sing Ging Abbot before passed away

551
00:25:22,500 --> 00:25:24,667
I then ascended Heaven and became a fairy
Follow me

552
00:25:24,667 --> 00:25:25,583
Guess what happened afterwards?

553
00:25:25,583 --> 00:25:27,792
The fairy became Dragon Fighter Lo Han

554
00:25:27,792 --> 00:25:28,583
That's me

555
00:25:28,583 --> 00:25:29,250
Follow me

556
00:25:29,250 --> 00:25:30,792
I came down on a mission

557
00:25:30,792 --> 00:25:32,375
As regards what the mission is,
you need not know

558
00:25:32,375 --> 00:25:34,417
You are at best a common person

559
00:25:34,417 --> 00:25:35,917
However, considering the length of your service,

560
00:25:35,917 --> 00:25:37,875
you've accumulated some worthiness
so I'll give you some face...

561
00:25:37,875 --> 00:25:41,000
...and address you as master
in front of your pupils

562
00:25:41,000 --> 00:25:41,875
Should give you due respect

563
00:25:41,875 --> 00:25:43,083
Go get me some clothes to change

564
00:25:43,458 --> 00:25:44,667
Master, he is mad

565
00:25:44,667 --> 00:25:45,750
So am

566
00:25:45,750 --> 00:25:47,125
I admire him on sight.

567
00:25:47,125 --> 00:25:48,708
- Bring me the clothes
- Yes

568
00:25:51,833 --> 00:25:52,833
You're lovely

569
00:25:55,667 --> 00:25:57,750
You've eaten all of it so quickly?

570
00:25:57,750 --> 00:25:59,417
There's a bigger one outside

571
00:26:01,583 --> 00:26:04,208
This is made of steel and can't be eaten

572
00:26:04,250 --> 00:26:05,917
Eat the drum behind

573
00:26:06,167 --> 00:26:08,042
I beg you not to bite, please

574
00:26:08,792 --> 00:26:09,750
Master

575
00:26:10,542 --> 00:26:11,667
Give me a priest name as in the
normal procedure

576
00:26:11,667 --> 00:26:13,208
You are so mad, I'll call you Mad Monk

577
00:26:13,708 --> 00:26:14,625
Very good

578
00:26:16,125 --> 00:26:21,500
Help! Don't chase me...

579
00:26:21,500 --> 00:26:22,750
A beggar for 9 lives?

580
00:26:23,375 --> 00:26:25,917
Don't

581
00:26:26,042 --> 00:26:30,083
Horrible! Really horrible

582
00:26:30,083 --> 00:26:31,875
What? Yun Ba Tin

583
00:26:31,958 --> 00:26:33,333
Hide quickly

584
00:26:35,625 --> 00:26:37,458
Hey, Yun is here!

585
00:26:37,667 --> 00:26:39,417
Hide in my home, quick

586
00:26:39,583 --> 00:26:40,667
Hey, God of Earth

587
00:26:44,667 --> 00:26:45,875
A villain of 9 lives?

588
00:26:46,792 --> 00:26:47,875
Save my time

589
00:26:51,750 --> 00:26:52,667
Help

590
00:26:53,500 --> 00:26:55,458
I told you not to let me see you

591
00:26:55,875 --> 00:26:59,167
A mere sight of you makes me so mad

592
00:26:59,250 --> 00:27:01,458
I don't want you to see me either. Keep away

593
00:27:01,458 --> 00:27:03,458
I wanted to avoid you, but couldn't

594
00:27:03,708 --> 00:27:05,458
You can hit my head,

595
00:27:05,458 --> 00:27:07,250
not the back

596
00:27:15,458 --> 00:27:16,958
Run? I'll burn down the temple,

597
00:27:16,958 --> 00:27:18,000
see if you can get away

598
00:27:18,083 --> 00:27:19,417
I'll burn you stinky monk too

599
00:27:23,958 --> 00:27:26,667
I want to burn you, how dare you
blow out my fire?

600
00:27:47,625 --> 00:27:48,708
You...

601
00:27:53,583 --> 00:27:54,625
Does it hurt?

602
00:27:55,000 --> 00:27:57,292
Now you know the agony of being bullied

603
00:27:57,792 --> 00:28:00,125
Lay down the sword and be 3 Buddha

604
00:28:00,542 --> 00:28:02,500
Don't be mad! Give you a kiss

605
00:28:03,250 --> 00:28:05,875
Take my advice and be a new person

606
00:28:05,917 --> 00:28:06,958
Good boy

607
00:28:11,417 --> 00:28:15,333
Impossible...

608
00:28:19,792 --> 00:28:21,125
Think over indoors.

609
00:28:21,125 --> 00:28:22,458
I'll come to you soon

610
00:28:26,083 --> 00:28:27,750
Don't be a beggar anymore. Go home with me

611
00:28:28,000 --> 00:28:29,583
What a horrible monster

612
00:28:30,833 --> 00:28:31,875
What are you afraid of?

613
00:28:31,875 --> 00:28:33,167
No, I'm not going

614
00:28:33,333 --> 00:28:34,458
Get going

615
00:28:40,542 --> 00:28:47,167
Brother. Milk... Brother. Milk.

616
00:28:47,375 --> 00:28:50,042
- Son, what happened to you?
- Bakbak

617
00:28:50,500 --> 00:28:52,167
I changed my hairstyle. Not bad, right?

618
00:28:52,583 --> 00:28:54,333
What happened to the house?

619
00:28:55,792 --> 00:28:56,833
(Li Sau Yun, I vow to kill your whole family)

620
00:28:56,833 --> 00:28:57,917
(Signed by Yun Ba Tin)

621
00:28:58,000 --> 00:29:01,500
Sau Yun, why mess with a character
like Yun Ba Tin?

622
00:29:01,500 --> 00:29:02,375
Bakbak

623
00:29:02,875 --> 00:29:03,542
Clean white white

624
00:29:03,542 --> 00:29:05,917
Li Sau Yun, I vow to kill your whole family

625
00:29:05,917 --> 00:29:07,125
Signed by Yun Ba Tin

626
00:29:07,125 --> 00:29:09,500
Master..., they killed all the poultries,

627
00:29:09,500 --> 00:29:11,042
even rats and roaches

628
00:29:11,042 --> 00:29:13,208
Also include a pregnant roach, so cruel

629
00:29:13,208 --> 00:29:15,042
Luckily you went to the temple
with master and madam

630
00:29:15,042 --> 00:29:17,167
Found out my background so soon. Great!

631
00:29:17,167 --> 00:29:18,833
Unfortunately I'm not Li Sau Yun anymore

632
00:29:19,083 --> 00:29:21,250
His calligraphy is good,
couldn't tell from appearance

633
00:29:21,542 --> 00:29:23,542
He even put down the date,

634
00:29:23,542 --> 00:29:25,625
such an organized person

635
00:29:25,625 --> 00:29:27,667
Son, look at the mess here,

636
00:29:27,667 --> 00:29:29,167
yet you're still concerned with such matters

637
00:29:30,958 --> 00:29:34,417
Master...

638
00:29:34,875 --> 00:29:36,792
Your dad won't make it

639
00:29:38,208 --> 00:29:41,792
Natural death is his good fortune. Let me see,

640
00:29:42,250 --> 00:29:44,917
he'll be an emperor in his next life.
Good for him

641
00:29:45,083 --> 00:29:47,667
Sau Yun..., are you crazy?

642
00:29:47,667 --> 00:29:50,083
Bingo, my new name is Mad Monk

643
00:29:51,833 --> 00:29:57,250
Heaven, what has our family done wrong?

644
00:29:57,250 --> 00:29:59,375
Yes, if you've done nothing wrong,

645
00:29:59,375 --> 00:30:01,375
you should die with him

646
00:30:03,542 --> 00:30:05,500
Madam...

647
00:30:05,500 --> 00:30:07,542
Give her some musk to smell, hurry

648
00:30:07,542 --> 00:30:08,292
Don't move

649
00:30:08,375 --> 00:30:10,125
Master and madam are fine, you shouldn't fiddle

650
00:30:10,125 --> 00:30:11,667
They're destined to become butterfly lover,

651
00:30:11,667 --> 00:30:12,792
and they always die together

652
00:30:13,208 --> 00:30:14,875
They'll continue their romance in the next life

653
00:30:14,875 --> 00:30:17,375
How admirable

654
00:30:17,375 --> 00:30:19,500
Young master, what should we do then?

655
00:30:19,500 --> 00:30:21,542
It's an auspicious affair,
get a chicken to celebrate

656
00:30:21,542 --> 00:30:23,625
And you, get an undertaker to give them a lift

657
00:30:23,958 --> 00:30:25,917
Go... Hurry...

658
00:30:25,917 --> 00:30:26,958
Let's go quickly

659
00:30:28,250 --> 00:30:30,375
- You can't go yet
- What?

660
00:30:30,625 --> 00:30:32,250
But you can sleep for a while

661
00:30:34,583 --> 00:30:35,542
Aiya...

662
00:30:36,667 --> 00:30:40,500
Fan...

663
00:30:47,917 --> 00:30:50,917
Good duckling... You two've lots of kids,

664
00:30:50,917 --> 00:30:52,542
why not give me one to fill my stomach

665
00:30:52,542 --> 00:30:54,542
If you don't shake your head
when I count to 3,

666
00:30:54,542 --> 00:30:55,042
that means you consent

667
00:30:55,042 --> 00:30:55,917
1,2,3

668
00:30:57,125 --> 00:30:58,542
- Aiya
- Outrageous

669
00:30:59,042 --> 00:30:59,958
You again?

670
00:30:59,958 --> 00:31:00,958
Sunk deep to a duck thief?

671
00:31:00,958 --> 00:31:03,583
You keep away! Keep away...

672
00:31:04,083 --> 00:31:05,208
I got the couple's consent

673
00:31:05,208 --> 00:31:06,292
Did you ask?

674
00:31:06,708 --> 00:31:07,833
Did he ask you?

675
00:31:07,833 --> 00:31:09,000
No...

676
00:31:09,458 --> 00:31:11,375
What? Duck can speak too?

677
00:31:11,375 --> 00:31:12,667
What more do you have to say?

678
00:31:13,083 --> 00:31:15,542
Stop pulling me...

679
00:31:15,542 --> 00:31:17,792
His mother must've seduced a parrot
that's why he could speak

680
00:31:18,083 --> 00:31:19,875
His mother has seduced a parrot?

681
00:31:19,875 --> 00:31:21,750
That's totally up to his mother

682
00:31:21,750 --> 00:31:24,292
Who asked you to meddle in it? I tell you,

683
00:31:24,292 --> 00:31:27,375
we must've self-respect as a human

684
00:31:27,917 --> 00:31:30,875
If you want to eat them,
you must get their consent first

685
00:31:31,083 --> 00:31:32,500
Who would consent to being eaten?

686
00:31:32,500 --> 00:31:33,458
Damn

687
00:31:33,708 --> 00:31:36,708
I want to eat you now
Whoever is willing can come with me

688
00:31:49,625 --> 00:31:53,625
80 great

689
00:31:54,375 --> 00:31:55,875
Worth to greet me as Master?

690
00:31:56,792 --> 00:32:01,000
Master, what can I do for you? Just let me know

691
00:32:01,083 --> 00:32:02,667
It's late, you should sleep

692
00:32:02,875 --> 00:32:07,958
Master, I am like a pig. I only sleep in daylight

693
00:32:11,292 --> 00:32:13,125
Dai Jung, your dad is here for you

694
00:32:13,250 --> 00:32:16,417
You mom finds you.
My dad died a long time ago

695
00:32:16,625 --> 00:32:17,583
Have a look

696
00:32:20,958 --> 00:32:24,458
Dad, how are you?

697
00:32:24,750 --> 00:32:26,875
Won't you listen to dad?

698
00:32:26,958 --> 00:32:27,875
Yes

699
00:32:27,958 --> 00:32:30,417
Then I advise you in dad's name,

700
00:32:30,417 --> 00:32:32,292
never go begging again with your bowl

701
00:32:32,292 --> 00:32:34,208
Dad, I've long yearned for this

702
00:32:34,208 --> 00:32:36,375
I want to get a bigger bowl to beg

703
00:32:37,375 --> 00:32:39,292
Outrageous

704
00:32:39,750 --> 00:32:41,500
Just now my dad came to see me

705
00:32:41,500 --> 00:32:44,167
Enough, go in and take a rest

706
00:32:45,167 --> 00:32:46,458
May throw out by the waiter

707
00:32:48,583 --> 00:32:49,875
Lots of gold

708
00:32:50,083 --> 00:32:50,958
Carry them

709
00:32:52,833 --> 00:32:54,458
Then you won't be thrown out

710
00:32:56,583 --> 00:32:58,292
Sir, this way please

711
00:32:58,333 --> 00:33:00,333
Get out, you stinking monk

712
00:33:00,333 --> 00:33:02,875
Sir, this way please

713
00:33:04,042 --> 00:33:06,125
Have a seat. I'll get some nice tea for you

714
00:33:07,125 --> 00:33:09,542
What would you like to eat? Tell them

715
00:33:09,833 --> 00:33:10,792
I want chicken butts

716
00:33:10,792 --> 00:33:12,042
Damn your ass!

717
00:33:12,042 --> 00:33:13,208
You have money now,

718
00:33:13,208 --> 00:33:14,667
you should order sharks' fins
to rinse your mouth

719
00:33:14,667 --> 00:33:15,792
Yes, right

720
00:33:16,000 --> 00:33:16,625
Order then

721
00:33:16,625 --> 00:33:18,708
Hey, I dare not. You order for me

722
00:33:18,708 --> 00:33:20,333
You lack confidence even in this,

723
00:33:20,333 --> 00:33:21,750
how are you going to be successful?

724
00:33:21,958 --> 00:33:23,208
Summon your courage

725
00:33:23,458 --> 00:33:24,792
Give me 2 days to consider

726
00:33:24,792 --> 00:33:26,542
Making fun of me? Speak

727
00:33:27,542 --> 00:33:28,583
I want...

728
00:33:28,583 --> 00:33:31,083
Louder, I want everyone to hear it

729
00:33:31,083 --> 00:33:32,167
Give me a bowl of butts...

730
00:33:32,167 --> 00:33:34,042
Not butts, sharks' fins

731
00:33:35,250 --> 00:33:36,708
Don't force me...

732
00:33:38,375 --> 00:33:41,583
Don't be silly! Why would I do that?

733
00:33:41,583 --> 00:33:43,208
Just say it and everything will be alright

734
00:33:44,000 --> 00:33:45,375
Do as I say

735
00:33:46,250 --> 00:33:47,958
But I really want to eat chicken butts

736
00:33:47,958 --> 00:33:49,750
Damn it! Fought back!

737
00:33:49,750 --> 00:33:50,833
I insist you to say...

738
00:33:50,833 --> 00:33:53,500
...give me a bowl of sharks' fins
to rinse my mouth. Say it

739
00:33:53,500 --> 00:33:57,708
Give me a bowl of sharks' fins
to rinse my mouth...

740
00:33:57,833 --> 00:33:58,958
You bastard

741
00:34:01,833 --> 00:34:04,083
- Yummy
- Outrageous

742
00:34:04,875 --> 00:34:07,417
Dai Jung, I won't talk any more nonsense

743
00:34:08,542 --> 00:34:09,375
Look

744
00:34:10,417 --> 00:34:13,208
This is my real self, Dragon Fighter Lo Han

745
00:34:13,208 --> 00:34:15,083
Ghost

746
00:34:15,083 --> 00:34:17,125
Stop screaming! A ghost is not like this

747
00:34:17,792 --> 00:34:20,500
It's like this

748
00:34:22,542 --> 00:34:24,667
Have you really passed out?

749
00:34:25,208 --> 00:34:27,500
Who's hitting my mouth?

750
00:34:27,500 --> 00:34:28,917
Disguised yourself in white top,

751
00:34:28,917 --> 00:34:30,500
and hanged two sausages on your mouth

752
00:34:30,500 --> 00:34:31,625
just to scare a beggar?

753
00:34:31,625 --> 00:34:33,042
You're a beast!

754
00:34:33,042 --> 00:34:35,125
Go to hell...

755
00:34:35,125 --> 00:34:36,458
- Stop it
- Don't stop me

756
00:34:36,458 --> 00:34:37,292
Let's go

757
00:34:37,292 --> 00:34:38,417
- Go to hell
- Don't be impetuous

758
00:34:38,417 --> 00:34:39,333
- Let's go
- Don't be mad

759
00:34:39,333 --> 00:34:41,500
- For such nuts, you've to beat him to dead
- Let's go

760
00:34:41,500 --> 00:34:43,000
People nowadays aren't frightened of ghosts

761
00:34:43,958 --> 00:34:44,875
Dai Jung

762
00:34:46,542 --> 00:34:47,375
Don't you understand now?

763
00:34:47,375 --> 00:34:48,458
Are you really a fairy?

764
00:34:48,458 --> 00:34:49,500
100%

765
00:34:49,500 --> 00:34:51,083
If you have any wishes, just let me know,

766
00:34:51,083 --> 00:34:52,500
I can fulfill for you. Tell me

767
00:34:52,500 --> 00:34:53,750
I want you to take me to Heaven

768
00:34:53,750 --> 00:34:54,792
What a fantastic wish

769
00:34:54,792 --> 00:34:56,375
I don't want to beg over here...

770
00:34:56,375 --> 00:34:57,417
any more

771
00:34:57,417 --> 00:35:00,208
At last I see you have pride

772
00:35:00,208 --> 00:35:00,833
I want to be...

773
00:35:00,833 --> 00:35:02,583
...a God of Beggar

774
00:35:02,583 --> 00:35:04,708
Outrageous...

775
00:35:07,292 --> 00:35:08,833
There'll be morning orisons tomorrow,

776
00:35:08,875 --> 00:35:10,375
let's rest early

777
00:35:10,375 --> 00:35:11,708
Master, what to do with the beggar outside?

778
00:35:11,875 --> 00:35:14,875
Buddha is merciful and the temple is
to serve people

779
00:35:14,875 --> 00:35:16,708
Let him stay outside for one night

780
00:35:16,708 --> 00:35:23,125
Milk...

781
00:35:23,125 --> 00:35:24,625
Hurry! Take them all inside

782
00:35:24,625 --> 00:35:25,667
Hey, you get the stuff

783
00:35:26,042 --> 00:35:30,833
Milk... Fish... Ya... Fish...

784
00:35:30,833 --> 00:35:31,958
Walk faster

785
00:35:32,250 --> 00:35:36,042
Brother... Milk...

786
00:35:36,042 --> 00:35:38,750
Bad boy, bearing a piece of BBQ pork
is better than having you

787
00:35:39,333 --> 00:35:40,333
BBQ pork?

788
00:35:45,083 --> 00:35:46,083
No...

789
00:35:46,667 --> 00:35:47,417
BBQ pork...

790
00:35:47,417 --> 00:35:49,042
I'm stunk! Don't eat me

791
00:35:54,542 --> 00:35:58,500
Tiger Fighter Lo Han transfigures

792
00:36:01,583 --> 00:36:02,583
Insulting me?

793
00:36:03,792 --> 00:36:05,292
You scared the piss out of me

794
00:36:08,458 --> 00:36:10,708
Unicorn, why look so miserable?

795
00:36:11,292 --> 00:36:13,417
I dressed up to hide my identity,

796
00:36:13,417 --> 00:36:14,875
so I can come down to inform you

797
00:36:14,875 --> 00:36:15,792
What's up?

798
00:36:15,792 --> 00:36:18,167
Heaven knew you've come down to
the mortal world,

799
00:36:18,167 --> 00:36:20,958
so they sent down God of Plague
to spread disease everywhere

800
00:36:20,958 --> 00:36:22,458
You'll bear the consequence of

801
00:36:22,458 --> 00:36:24,333
the casualties caused

802
00:36:25,000 --> 00:36:27,500
For the evil done, by that time,

803
00:36:27,500 --> 00:36:29,667
you may be demoted 3 grades

804
00:36:29,667 --> 00:36:31,208
Wake up again, Tiger Fighter

805
00:36:31,208 --> 00:36:33,375
Dragon Fighter, this is not my fault

806
00:36:33,375 --> 00:36:34,167
Though it might not be,

807
00:36:34,167 --> 00:36:36,042
you know how it's like with the fools up there

808
00:36:36,042 --> 00:36:37,542
It matters little if one is downgraded,

809
00:36:37,542 --> 00:36:39,375
but to harm so many lives,

810
00:36:39,375 --> 00:36:40,292
it's really a big trouble

811
00:36:40,292 --> 00:36:41,000
That's right...

812
00:36:41,333 --> 00:36:42,792
What rule is that?

813
00:36:42,792 --> 00:36:44,792
Tell me, who ordered to spread the plague?

814
00:36:44,792 --> 00:36:45,667
A high directive

815
00:36:45,667 --> 00:36:46,708
Damn it

816
00:36:46,917 --> 00:36:48,458
Hey, which department?

817
00:36:49,458 --> 00:36:50,500
Tell us,

818
00:36:50,500 --> 00:36:52,042
we promise not to accuse you

819
00:36:52,042 --> 00:36:53,333
The Recreation Department

820
00:36:53,333 --> 00:36:56,125
What? They are responsible for travels though

821
00:36:56,125 --> 00:36:58,625
They are linked to the Accounts Department

822
00:36:58,625 --> 00:37:00,458
- The Accounts Department pays salaries only
- Yes

823
00:37:00,458 --> 00:37:01,583
That's right

824
00:37:01,625 --> 00:37:03,792
The trouble is Accounts and

825
