00:51:48,958 --> 00:51:50,208
What would you like?

1094
00:51:50,750 --> 00:51:53,375
A plate of chicken butts would be nice

1095
00:51:54,500 --> 00:51:55,833
Anything wrong?

1096
00:51:56,125 --> 00:51:57,000
You're an epicure

1097
00:52:02,708 --> 00:52:03,792
What do you do?

1098
00:52:04,000 --> 00:52:06,292
- I'm a beggar
- What?

1099
00:52:07,208 --> 00:52:08,833
So it's you

1100
00:52:09,167 --> 00:52:10,625
Do you mind?

1101
00:52:11,250 --> 00:52:14,250
Why would I?
When I see you it's like seeing that guy

1102
00:52:14,250 --> 00:52:15,125
Where's that guy?

1103
00:52:15,125 --> 00:52:16,417
That guy asked me to come

1104
00:52:16,417 --> 00:52:17,917
Why he asked you to come?

1105
00:52:17,917 --> 00:52:19,917
That guy asks me here to...

1106
00:52:21,125 --> 00:52:22,375
...buy bean curd

1107
00:52:22,625 --> 00:52:24,375
You're so naughty

1108
00:52:33,583 --> 00:52:35,542
Good! I'll fix you too

1109
00:52:43,625 --> 00:52:46,333
With the possession of Shaolin Patriarch Dhama,
in a lamp's time,

1110
00:52:46,333 --> 00:52:48,083
there's no reason I can't fix you

1111
00:52:48,542 --> 00:52:49,500
Halt

1112
00:52:49,792 --> 00:52:50,333
Sock him

1113
00:52:50,333 --> 00:52:50,875
Yes

1114
00:52:57,208 --> 00:53:01,500
What happened... Look...what happened?

1115
00:53:02,292 --> 00:53:03,417
Really powerful

1116
00:53:04,042 --> 00:53:05,250
Patriarch Dhama?

1117
00:53:06,792 --> 00:53:07,958
Are you scared?

1118
00:53:07,958 --> 00:53:10,708
You are deep in sin

1119
00:53:10,708 --> 00:53:11,792
Consider this as doing charity,

1120
00:53:11,792 --> 00:53:13,500
I'll take you back to be a monk

1121
00:53:13,500 --> 00:53:14,500
Damn you

1122
00:53:15,333 --> 00:53:16,875
I'll beat you till you come with me

1123
00:53:20,333 --> 00:53:22,167
Joking... A rattan cane

1124
00:53:24,292 --> 00:53:25,417
Look down on me?

1125
00:53:25,417 --> 00:53:26,500
Scared now?

1126
00:53:27,417 --> 00:53:28,833
I'm tired

1127
00:53:31,500 --> 00:53:34,125
Go...

1128
00:53:37,750 --> 00:53:38,708
See where you can run to?

1129
00:53:42,833 --> 00:53:44,625
Damn it! Never listen

1130
00:54:31,708 --> 00:54:34,458
- Reconciled to defeat yet?
- Reconciled to the hell of you

1131
00:54:45,500 --> 00:54:47,083
So, that guy is a fairy?

1132
00:54:47,083 --> 00:54:48,917
I thought you knew

1133
00:54:48,917 --> 00:54:51,042
Sorry for troubling you

1134
00:54:51,042 --> 00:54:52,250
Never mind. I enjoy it...

1135
00:54:52,750 --> 00:54:53,583
How many?

1136
00:54:53,583 --> 00:54:55,125
For a situation like this, two will suffice

1137
00:54:56,417 --> 00:54:58,042
Remember to tell that guy I'll sell soy milk

1138
00:54:58,042 --> 00:54:59,833
as well tomorrow

1139
00:54:59,833 --> 00:55:00,750
Really?

1140
00:55:01,125 --> 00:55:03,625
Do you think he'll like it salty or sweet?

1141
00:55:03,625 --> 00:55:04,375
Salty

1142
00:55:04,375 --> 00:55:05,667
Best to add some preserved savory vegetables

1143
00:55:05,792 --> 00:55:07,083
Even better with sesame seeds

1144
00:55:07,458 --> 00:55:09,333
Lo Han soy milk

1145
00:55:09,333 --> 00:55:10,500
He likes dog meat

1146
00:55:10,500 --> 00:55:12,833
Dog meat Lo Han soy milk

1147
00:55:13,625 --> 00:55:15,250
Yeah”.

1148
00:55:17,833 --> 00:55:20,000
Siu Yuk's unbeatable soy milk

1149
00:55:20,000 --> 00:55:21,000
Yeah”.

1150
00:55:21,000 --> 00:55:23,917
I've come for a whore

1151
00:55:32,917 --> 00:55:34,833
As matters stand, I have to fight
violence with violence

1152
00:55:36,750 --> 00:55:37,833
Iron Head

1153
00:55:49,875 --> 00:55:51,125
Reconciled to defeat now?

1154
00:55:51,708 --> 00:55:54,042
I only want you to be a monk, not go to hell

1155
00:55:54,042 --> 00:55:55,417
Be good and come with me now

1156
00:56:00,417 --> 00:56:02,458
You're simply incorrigible

1157
00:56:05,917 --> 00:56:07,583
Ok... forget about being a monk

1158
00:56:07,583 --> 00:56:09,167
Just refrain from killing people, okay?

1159
00:56:16,125 --> 00:56:18,958
Damn! Are you a human being or a beast?

1160
00:56:26,708 --> 00:56:27,750
Do you like me?

1161
00:56:27,750 --> 00:56:28,375
I do

1162
00:56:28,375 --> 00:56:29,417
But, make it next life

1163
00:56:29,500 --> 00:56:32,458
This life, I've to marry that guy

1164
00:56:32,458 --> 00:56:33,958
You're right. I found my self-respect

1165
00:56:33,958 --> 00:56:35,500
after knowing him too

1166
00:56:41,792 --> 00:56:43,417
OK, you're on the upside tonight

1167
00:56:43,417 --> 00:56:44,708
Let's compromise! If you back off

1168
00:56:44,708 --> 00:56:45,833
and leave Siu Yuk alone tonight,

1169
00:56:45,833 --> 00:56:47,458
we'll settle our score later

1170
00:56:55,417 --> 00:56:58,375
If I hadn't changed to Patriarch Dhama,
I'd have been killed by you

1171
00:56:58,625 --> 00:57:00,083
You bastard

1172
00:57:00,750 --> 00:57:02,417
Can't bear with it anymore

1173
00:57:14,292 --> 00:57:16,833
Buddha is merciful! Good luck

1174
00:57:27,000 --> 00:57:30,708
Shit! Dai Jung, it's time

1175
00:57:32,417 --> 00:57:33,708
ls someone selling rice dumplings?

1176
00:57:33,833 --> 00:57:34,750
That stand's there every day.

1177
00:57:34,750 --> 00:57:35,875
- Never mind it
- Ok

1178
00:57:38,625 --> 00:57:41,667
Magic is over! Let's go

1179
00:57:42,250 --> 00:57:44,250
Shit! Time is up

1180
00:57:46,667 --> 00:57:48,500
Aiya... I changed back to a beggar

1181
00:57:48,500 --> 00:57:50,750
Why shout? You are in fact a beggar

1182
00:57:51,708 --> 00:57:52,875
I have to go

1183
00:57:53,250 --> 00:57:56,083
Hey, are we good friends?

1184
00:57:58,625 --> 00:58:00,083
Why haven't you come down yet... you really...

1185
00:58:00,083 --> 00:58:00,958
Hey man

1186
00:58:02,042 --> 00:58:04,167
Have you seen someone with a big beard?

1187
00:58:04,625 --> 00:58:06,583
Yes, he seems over there in the toilet

1188
00:58:07,000 --> 00:58:07,792
After him

1189
00:58:08,583 --> 00:58:09,542
Halt

1190
00:58:10,167 --> 00:58:11,542
Man, you look familiar

1191
00:58:12,750 --> 00:58:14,875
Heroes, you're mistaken

1192
00:58:20,917 --> 00:58:21,875
Outrageous!

1193
00:58:21,875 --> 00:58:23,583
I warned you not to let me see you

1194
00:58:23,583 --> 00:58:24,667
Don't...

1195
00:58:25,083 --> 00:58:26,292
Sponge as well?

1196
00:58:26,583 --> 00:58:28,875
No, I didn't

1197
00:58:28,875 --> 00:58:30,250
I have money

1198
00:58:30,917 --> 00:58:32,292
Shit! The gold changed...

1199
00:58:40,333 --> 00:58:42,875
Don't beat him! He's not a sponger

1200
00:58:43,333 --> 00:58:44,458
He's my boyfriend

1201
00:58:44,458 --> 00:58:46,542
That cheap? You even want one with sores?

1202
00:58:49,167 --> 00:58:50,125
Look

1203
00:58:51,167 --> 00:58:52,792
Big brother, I told you it wasn't me

1204
00:58:52,792 --> 00:58:53,708
You still deny it?

1205
00:58:53,708 --> 00:58:55,458
Don't be mad! Maybe it's just likeness

1206
00:58:55,458 --> 00:58:56,833
You're pretending

1207
00:58:56,833 --> 00:58:58,167
Do I look like that moustached Singh?

1208
00:58:58,167 --> 00:58:58,875
Maybe you shaved it off?

1209
00:58:58,875 --> 00:59:00,417
Who could do it so quickly?

1210
00:59:00,417 --> 00:59:02,042
You're siding with a stranger

1211
00:59:02,042 --> 00:59:03,083
I talk sense

1212
00:59:03,083 --> 00:59:04,000
Go to hell

1213
00:59:05,708 --> 00:59:06,750
See! You've hurt someone

1214
00:59:06,750 --> 00:59:07,542
What? Getting mad?

1215
00:59:07,542 --> 00:59:09,042
What? Should I stand here and let you hit me?

1216
00:59:09,167 --> 00:59:09,875
What? You dare disobey what the big brother
tells you to do?

1217
00:59:09,875 --> 00:59:10,583
What? A big one bullies a small one?

1218
00:59:10,625 --> 00:59:11,750
- I've endured for a long time.
- Go to hell

1219
00:59:11,750 --> 00:59:15,458
Don't beat my big brother! Go away

1220
00:59:15,458 --> 00:59:19,167
Damn it! Again! Don't... Hey...

1221
00:59:19,292 --> 00:59:20,500
Don't

1222
00:59:20,500 --> 00:59:21,375
Help

1223
00:59:21,375 --> 00:59:22,708
Don't, master

1224
00:59:23,125 --> 00:59:24,250
Let her go please, master

1225
00:59:29,583 --> 00:59:30,542
Siu Yuk...

1226
00:59:34,125 --> 00:59:36,792
Help

1227
00:59:38,250 --> 00:59:40,083
Big head

1228
00:59:44,667 --> 00:59:45,875
Dai Jung

1229
00:59:47,333 --> 00:59:48,667
Why didn't you knock?

1230
00:59:48,958 --> 00:59:49,917
Sorry, I got the wrong place

1231
00:59:50,125 --> 00:59:51,250
Close the door

1232
00:59:51,792 --> 00:59:52,500
Have a banana

1233
00:59:52,583 --> 00:59:53,750
Sorry...

1234
00:59:56,333 --> 00:59:57,625
Master...

1235
00:59:58,125 --> 00:59:59,625
What's taken you so long? Wanna die?

1236
00:59:59,625 --> 01:00:00,875
Things changed back to original! Let's go

1237
01:00:00,875 --> 01:00:02,833
Master, I can't move

1238
01:00:11,542 --> 01:00:13,292
What? Yun Ba Tin

1239
01:00:19,292 --> 01:00:20,958
Go to hell, Beggar Dai Jung

1240
01:00:25,667 --> 01:00:26,833
Don't call me Dai Jung

1241
01:00:27,417 --> 01:00:29,375
Call me Chow Yat Cheung

1242
01:00:35,958 --> 01:00:36,917
Dai Jung

1243
01:00:38,500 --> 01:00:39,583
You've made us suffer a lot

1244
01:00:39,583 --> 01:00:41,125
Dai Jung... you can't die!

1245
01:00:41,125 --> 01:00:41,792
You must hang on

1246
01:00:41,792 --> 01:00:43,583
Dai Jung... you can't die! Dai Jung

1247
01:00:43,583 --> 01:00:45,125
You've no more magical powers?

1248
01:00:45,125 --> 01:00:47,000
Tomorrow, I'll show you tomorrow

1249
01:00:54,208 --> 01:00:55,500
Kill you, son of the bitch

1250
01:00:55,708 --> 01:00:58,458
- Turn his face over
- Turn his face

1251
01:01:00,250 --> 01:01:01,208
Look

1252
01:01:10,167 --> 01:01:11,542
Open his eyes

1253
01:01:17,792 --> 01:01:21,042
Master Tin said to let you go,
but be careful in future

1254
01:01:21,042 --> 01:01:22,750
What a show it was just now
You didn't even blink

1255
01:01:22,833 --> 01:01:24,125
Frankly... it was fascinating

1256
01:01:24,125 --> 01:01:25,083
Yes

1257
01:01:28,792 --> 01:01:32,500
You'll surely die this time

1258
01:01:34,708 --> 01:01:35,667
God of Earth

1259
01:01:37,375 --> 01:01:41,458
God of Earth, where are you? Come out quickly

1260
01:01:43,250 --> 01:01:46,500
Hey... I'm here. Why shouting so loud?

1261
01:01:46,500 --> 01:01:48,042
How can I save Dai Jung?

1262
01:01:48,333 --> 01:01:52,250
A man's fate is pre- determined
One can't change Heaven's rules

1263
01:01:52,250 --> 01:01:53,458
But he has suffered
an innocent death because of me

1264
01:01:53,458 --> 01:01:54,792
I've to bring him back no matter what

1265
01:01:54,792 --> 01:01:56,042
Help me to think some ways

1266
01:01:56,042 --> 01:01:57,750
An innocent death means going to hell

1267
01:01:58,500 --> 01:02:00,750
King of Hades is strict

1268
01:02:01,083 --> 01:02:02,083
But...

1269
01:02:02,500 --> 01:02:03,500
Speak up

1270
01:02:03,708 --> 01:02:05,833
Before entering the City of Innocent Deaths,

1271
01:02:05,833 --> 01:02:08,375
There's an area governed by
evil god Hak Lo Sat

1272
01:02:08,917 --> 01:02:10,917
He admits stray spirits

1273
01:02:11,417 --> 01:02:13,708
Anyone in his hands never gets reincarnated

1274
01:02:14,333 --> 01:02:16,333
But you may talk it over with him

1275
01:02:16,333 --> 01:02:17,625
Bring me down to him quickly

1276
01:02:17,625 --> 01:02:21,125
Hey... I'm only a junior god and thus
not eligible to go down

1277
01:02:21,125 --> 01:02:23,875
Unlike you, you've a golden body for protection

1278
01:02:23,875 --> 01:02:25,625
which makes you invulnerable

1279
01:02:26,542 --> 01:02:27,875
I'll go and get back the golden body now

1280
01:02:27,875 --> 01:02:30,958
Hey... don't make fun of the golden body

1281
01:02:30,958 --> 01:02:32,042
I must do what's necessary

1282
01:02:38,083 --> 01:02:39,083
What're you doing? Let go

1283
01:02:39,083 --> 01:02:41,000
Master said this golden body cannot
leave the temple

1284
01:02:41,000 --> 01:02:43,333
What if it does?

1285
01:02:43,333 --> 01:02:44,417
- I don't know
- Then that means it's okay

1286
01:02:44,417 --> 01:02:46,167
Let me borrow it, I'll pay you lots of interest

1287
01:02:46,542 --> 01:02:47,792
- No
- For just one night

1288
01:02:47,792 --> 01:02:48,750
- No
- One hour

1289
01:02:48,750 --> 01:02:50,167
- No
- Ok, then a cross

1290
01:02:50,167 --> 01:02:51,667
What cross?

1291
01:03:49,375 --> 01:03:50,417
Hey man, halt

1292
01:03:50,417 --> 01:03:51,500
Stand still

1293
01:03:51,833 --> 01:03:52,875
What's the matter?

1294
01:03:54,125 --> 01:03:55,000
Let him go

1295
01:03:55,042 --> 01:03:56,958
Are you the Buddha?

1296
01:03:56,958 --> 01:03:57,542
No

1297
01:03:57,542 --> 01:03:58,333
Damn

1298
01:04:07,375 --> 01:04:09,958
Man, you're so rude. Let me tell you

1299
01:04:09,958 --> 01:04:11,208
I'm friends with the Buddha

1300
01:04:11,500 --> 01:04:13,500
I'll retrieve this person's spirit
on his behalf,

1301
01:04:13,500 --> 01:04:14,542
understand?

1302
01:04:16,875 --> 01:04:18,250
How dare you? Stop

1303
01:04:18,250 --> 01:04:19,042
Stop

1304
01:04:31,792 --> 01:04:34,292
Rubbish! Ask Sakyamuni to see me

1305
01:04:35,958 --> 01:04:37,583
Don't go...

1306
01:04:38,083 --> 01:04:40,542
In fact, I'm not on good terms with Buddha

1307
01:04:40,917 --> 01:04:42,917
I didn't know you and he had a grudge

1308
01:04:43,500 --> 01:04:44,750
I'll take you for big brother

1309
01:04:44,750 --> 01:04:47,458
Since you've so many men under you,
having one more doesn't make a difference

1310
01:04:47,458 --> 01:04:49,667
This one... treat this as a gift to me

1311
01:04:49,667 --> 01:04:51,875
What's in it for me?

1312
01:04:51,875 --> 01:04:52,792
What's in it?

1313
01:04:53,500 --> 01:04:56,375
How about... I'll pedicure for you,
the nails are so long,

1314
01:04:56,375 --> 01:04:57,208
okay?

1315
01:04:57,458 --> 01:05:01,583
Damn! Unless you exchange it
with your golden body

1316
01:05:01,917 --> 01:05:04,292
Golden body? I can't give it to you

1317
01:05:04,292 --> 01:05:05,667
Besides, you've no use for it

1318
01:05:06,083 --> 01:05:07,250
Just as a display

1319
01:05:07,250 --> 01:05:09,417
Bastard, you're going too far

1320
01:05:09,417 --> 01:05:11,167
Okay, exchange

1321
01:05:14,125 --> 01:05:16,208
Dai Jung, I must bring you back by any means

1322
01:05:16,583 --> 01:05:17,417
Don't worry

1323
01:05:17,417 --> 01:05:18,708
Put down your golden body

1324
01:05:44,500 --> 01:05:45,875
You promised to exchange with me

1325
01:05:45,875 --> 01:05:47,375
Why have you taken his spirit?

1326
01:05:47,375 --> 01:05:48,792
I'm a baddie

1327
01:06:02,625 --> 01:06:05,292
Stinking monk, why appeared so sudden

1328
01:06:05,292 --> 01:06:06,875
Damn, I'm back

1329
01:06:06,875 --> 01:06:08,917
If you don't like it, you can go back down

1330
01:06:08,917 --> 01:06:11,042
How could I go down without the golden body?

1331
01:06:11,292 --> 01:06:12,667
What a pity!

1332
01:06:12,667 --> 01:06:13,917
He's even cheated me out of my golden body

1333
01:06:14,417 --> 01:06:15,875
Dai Jung...

1334
01:06:16,417 --> 01:06:18,042
Dai Jung...

1335
01:06:21,958 --> 01:06:23,208
Dai Jung...

1336
01:07:03,833 --> 01:07:07,000
Lord, I'll do as you instruct me

1337
01:07:07,750 --> 01:07:09,583
and help accomplish your mission

1338
01:07:22,833 --> 01:07:26,583
Hey... don't be like that?

1339
01:07:26,583 --> 01:07:27,875
Hey... brothers...

1340
01:07:29,417 --> 01:07:30,917
Won't give me a face?

1341
01:07:31,292 --> 01:07:33,125
I'm in charge here

1342
01:07:34,958 --> 01:07:36,208
I told you not to do this

1343
01:07:36,208 --> 01:07:37,292
What's the matter?

1344
01:07:37,708 --> 01:07:39,458
As you have consorted with evil spirits,

1345
01:07:39,458 --> 01:07:41,667
the fairies inside said...

1346
01:07:41,667 --> 01:07:43,667
...they don't want to be with you

1347
01:07:43,875 --> 01:07:47,292
They've all gone
These just returned to get their luggage

1348
01:07:47,417 --> 01:07:49,583
Sorry, for my life-long emoluments,

1349
01:07:49,583 --> 01:07:51,583
I have to follow them... goodbye

1350
01:08:03,125 --> 01:08:06,542
What's happening? Where's the stuff?

1351
01:08:07,625 --> 01:08:09,042
Mad Monk, where's the golden body?

1352
01:08:11,208 --> 01:08:13,333
Oh no! You've caused a big trouble

1353
01:08:17,042 --> 01:08:19,083
On no! Even God of Earth is gone.

1354
01:08:19,083 --> 01:08:20,167
We're in deep shit now

1355
01:08:20,208 --> 01:08:21,750
Oh no...

1356
01:08:38,833 --> 01:08:40,250
Master, where are you going?

1357
01:08:40,500 --> 01:08:42,417
Mad Monk, as I told you,

1358
01:08:42,417 --> 01:08:44,417
the golden body cannot leave the temple

1359
01:08:44,417 --> 01:08:46,333
Now you've caused anger among men and gods

1360
01:08:46,333 --> 01:08:48,292
how can I bear this responsibility?

1361
01:08:49,042 --> 01:08:50,208
Master, leave quickly

1362
01:08:50,208 --> 01:08:52,583
A thunder may split the temple

1363
01:09:00,083 --> 01:09:02,833
- You blame me too?
- Let's go... even the Goddess are down.

1364
